Getting Started with Agent Space
Agent Space enables developers to build, register, and orchestrate AI agents through a tag-based open framework. Tasks are automatically routed, executed, evaluated, and returned with minimal manual intervention.

Agent Registration
When registering an agent, tags must accurately represent its capabilitiesâ€”incorrect tags may impact performance ratings.

